	(752,172,'_form','<div class=\"customerfeedback\">\n<div class=\"td pull-left\"><span class=\"labl\">Phone Reception</span><div id=\"phone-reception\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"td pull-right\"><span class=\"labl\">Billing </span><div id=\"billing\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"td pull-left\"><span class=\"labl\">Website </span><div id=\"website\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"td pull-right\"><span class=\"labl veh\">Vehicle<br>Appearance</span><div id=\"vehicle-appearance\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"td pull-left\"><span class=\"labl\">Driver </span><div id=\"driver\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"td pull-right\"><span class=\"labl\">overal</span><div id=\"overal\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n<div class=\"tr\">Comments (optional)<br>[textarea experience-1]</div><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"subtitle text-center uppdercase\">Driver</h2>\n<div class=\"customerfeedback\"><div class=\"td pull-left\"><span class=\"labl\">Timeliness</span><div id=\"timeliness\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"td pull-right\"><span class=\"labl\">Safety</span><div id=\"safety\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"td pull-left\"><span class=\"labl veh\">Driver<br>Knowledge</span><div id=\"driver-knowledge\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"td pull-right\"><span class=\"labl\">Professionalism</span><div id=\"professionalism\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"td pull-left\"><span class=\"labl veh\">Personal<br>Apperance</span><div id=\"personal-apperance\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div><div class=\"tr\">Comments (optional) <br>[textarea experience-2]</div>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"subtitle text-center uppdercase\">Vehicle </h2>\n<div class=\"customerfeedback\">\n<div class=\"td pull-left\"><span class=\"labl veh\">Interior<br>Appearance</span><div id=\"interior-appearance\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"td pull-right\"><span class=\"labl veh\">Exterior<br>Appearance</span><div id=\"exterior-appearance\" class=\"pull-right rate\" data-score=\"1\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n<div class=\"tr\">Comments (optional) <br>[textarea experience-3]</div>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"customerfeedback\">\n<strong>Final Comments</strong><br>\n<div class=\"spacer\"></div>\n<div>As part of our commitment to enhancing your customer experience, we are always interested in hearing ways in which we can enhance our services to better suit your needs.  Please provide your general comments about your experience with Legends Limousine and any other information that will enable us to maintain the region\'s highest quality transportation service.</div>\n<div class=\"tr\">Comments (optional) <br>[textarea experience-4]</div>\n<div class=\"tr\">Are you a first time customer?</div>\n<div>[radio firsttime-customer use_label_element \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n<div class=\"tr\">Did you find our website to be informative and easy to use?</div>\n<div>[radio special-accommodations use_label_element \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n<div class=\"tr\">If you requested any special accommodations, were they met to your satisfaction?</div>\n<div>[radio special-accommodations use_label_element \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n<div class=\"tr\">Would you recommend Legends Limousine to a friend/family/co-worker?</div>\n<div>[radio recommend-us use_label_element \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n<div class=\"tr\">Would you be interested in any additional information about our services?</div>\n<div>[radio additional-information use_label_element \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n<div class=\"tr\">How did you hear about Legends Limousine?</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">[select hearus class:btn-block include_blank \"Friend\" \"Colleague\" \"Google\" \"Yahoo\" \"Bing\" \"Newspaper\" \"Valpak\" \"Direct Mail\" \"E-mail\" \"Yellow Pages\" \"Other\"]</div>\n</div>\n<div><strong>Information Required</strong></div>\n<div class=\"spacer\"></div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">[text* first-name class:btn-block placeholder \"First Name\"]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">[text* last-name class:btn-block placeholder \"Last Name\"]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">    \n<div class=\"span6\">[email* your-email class:btn-block placeholder \"email\"]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"spacer\"></div>\n<div class=\"spacer\"></div>\n<input class=\"butn\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div>'),
