nds’ dispatchers will direct you to a curbside point located right outside your terminal where you will meet your driver within a few minutes.\r\n4. If you do not call us to meet your driver after 45 minutes, we will try to contact you on the telephone number provided. If we still fail to reach you, the car will be dismissed and you will be billed for a “No Show”.\r\n\r\n<strong>*Please note when reserving a stretch limo, a suv, or 13 pass van, the inside pick up is the only option available.* </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>*Please note that a credit card is required for all airport pick-ups to secure your reservation and it is your choice whether to use the card for payment at the end of the trip or you can pay cash. Legends will obtain an authorization approximately 25% above the estimated quote to cover any additional charges such as: waiting time, additional stops, gratuity, tolls, etc. Also please note, if you are using a debit card, there will be a temporary hold of the estimate quote plus 25% for approximately three to five business days until the actual charge is processed. </strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Contact us from the airport:</strong>\r\nMain Line: 1(718)788-1234\r\nToll Free: 1(888)LEGENDS 1(888)534-3637\r\nToll Free: 1(800)788-2119','New York Airport Limo Service','','inherit','open','open','','5-revision-v1','','','2013-09-04 13:48:35','2013-09-04 13:48:35','',5,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(7,1,'2013-09-04 13:48:54','2013-09-04 13:48:54','<div id=\"homeBottomContentText\">\r\n\r\nOuter borough travel? Not to worry. Legends Limousine is your premiere Brooklyn car service. Our punctuality and performance extends well beyond Manhattan, making us one of New York City’s most well-reputed limousine services. For dependable service from Park Slope to Boerum Hill, Brooklyn Heights to Carroll Gardens, and beyond, be sure to call Legends Limousine first.  \r\n\r\nBrooklyn locals are among our most loyal clients, enjoying our excellent Brooklyn transport services at affordable rates.  In particular, Legends Limousine is among the most established limousine services in Red Hook, Sunset Park, and Fort Greene.  For both personal and corporate use, we offer secure, easy-to-use accounts.  And our superior dispatch technology means we’ll always get to you quickly.  \r\n\r\nThe safety and satisfaction of our clients are Legends Limousine’s chief concerns.  All of our drivers and vehicles are 100% licensed and insured.  No comprehensive Brooklyn car service can match our impeccable safety record and 20 years of experience and seamless service.  Our staff counts the city’s savviest, most experienced chauffeurs, with unmatched knowledge of the tri-state area, among its ranks. Thanks to them, Legends Limousine has enjoyed decades as one of Brooklyn’s most highly regarded car services.  We offer a wide range of transportation services that are specifically designed with you in mind, and we can tailor all your trips to your transportation needs. From special events to corporate travel, Legends Limousine is proud to be your premiere Brooklyn car service. \r\n\r\n\r\n</div>','Brooklyn Car Service','','publish','open','open','','brooklyn-car-service','','','2014-06-23 15:42:07','2014-06-23 15:42:07','',0,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/?page_id=7',28,'page','',0),
