	(453,1,'2014-06-23 15:44:01','2014-06-23 15:44:01','What could be better than a one-of-a-kind adventure in New York, complete with your own driver? Customize your time in New York City with our unique sightseeing tours, and see Manhattan as you never have before.  We offer you the flexibility to choose between a tried-and-true set route, which will take you all around the island in a day, or we can tailor your trip to your exact specifications.  Either way, our goal is to exceed your expectations.   \r\n\r\nOur clients enjoy traveling in beautifully appointed vehicles throughout the course of their excursions. In order for you to see everything you desire, your driver will be happy to make as many stops as you’d like, waiting as long as necessary at each location along the way.  Whether you want to check out hot spots from television shows, get to a few museums, or indulge in some of the best shopping around, Legends Limousine can create and deliver an ideal sightseeing itinerary to meet all your needs. \r\n\r\nRadio City Music Hall, Central Park, and the Empire State Building await your arrival (and don’t forget the world’s most exclusive fashion meccas and in-demand restaurants).  Create your own customized tour, and never worry about missing out on anything New York City has to offer.  Just call Legends Limousine to schedule your very own sightseeing excursion.  Our professional staff will help you leave behind the hassle and uncertainty of planning an action-packed day in one of the world’s busiest cities. Enjoy the flexibility and ease of a personal vehicle with an experienced driver, and relish every moment in the Big Apple.','Sightseeing','','inherit','open','open','','57-revision-v1','','','2014-06-23 15:44:01','2014-06-23 15:44:01','',57,'http://www.spidadesign.us/legends/57-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
